#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an4.113"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.113:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.113:0.2"
msgid "12. Kesivagga "
msgstr "12. With Kesi "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: assājānīya-patodasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.113:0.3"
msgid "113. Patodasutta "
msgstr "113. The Goad "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.113:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, bhadrā assājānīyā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four fine thoroughbreds are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.113:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.113:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco bhadro assājānīyo patodacchāyaṃ disvā saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati: "
msgstr "One fine thoroughbred is moved to act when it sees the shadow of the goad, thinking: "

#. VAR: kimassāhaṃ → kathamassāhaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an4.113:1.4"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu kho maṃ ajja assadammasārathi kāraṇaṃ kāressati, kimassāhaṃ paṭikaromī’ti. "
msgstr "‘What task will the horse trainer have me do today? How should I respond?’ "

msgctxt "an4.113:1.5"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbreds are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:1.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo bhadro assājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the first fine thoroughbred found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an4.113:2.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo na heva kho patodacchāyaṃ disvā saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati, api ca kho lomavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, one fine thoroughbred isn’t moved to act when it sees the shadow of the goad, but only when its hairs are struck, thinking: "

msgctxt "an4.113:2.2"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu kho maṃ ajja assadammasārathi kāraṇaṃ kāressati, kimassāhaṃ paṭikaromī’ti. "
msgstr "‘What task will the horse trainer have me do today? How should I respond?’ "

msgctxt "an4.113:2.3"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbreds are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:2.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo bhadro assājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the second fine thoroughbred found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an4.113:3.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo na heva kho patodacchāyaṃ disvā saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati nāpi lomavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati, api ca kho cammavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, one fine thoroughbred isn’t moved to act when it sees the shadow of the goad, nor when its hairs are struck, but only when its hide is struck, thinking: "

msgctxt "an4.113:3.2"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu kho maṃ ajja assadammasārathi kāraṇaṃ kāressati, kimassāhaṃ paṭikaromī’ti. "
msgstr "‘What task will the horse trainer have me do today? How should I respond?’ "

msgctxt "an4.113:3.3"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbreds are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo bhadro assājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the third fine thoroughbred found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.115, sc4
msgctxt "an4.113:4.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo na heva kho patodacchāyaṃ disvā saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati nāpi lomavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati nāpi cammavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati, api ca kho aṭṭhivedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati: "
msgstr "Furthermore, one fine thoroughbred isn’t moved to act when it sees the shadow of the goad, nor when its hairs are struck, nor when its hide is struck, but only when its bone is struck, thinking: "

msgctxt "an4.113:4.2"
msgid "‘kiṃ nu kho maṃ ajja assadammasārathi kāraṇaṃ kāressati, kimassāhaṃ paṭikaromī’ti. "
msgstr "‘What task will the horse trainer have me do today? How should I respond?’ "

msgctxt "an4.113:4.3"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro assājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbreds are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:4.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho bhadro assājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the fourth fine thoroughbred found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.113:4.5"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro bhadrā assājānīyā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "These are the four fine thoroughbreds found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an4.113:5.1"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, cattārome bhadrā purisājānīyā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "In the same way, these four fine thoroughbred people are found in the world. "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro? "
msgstr "What four? "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.113:5.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco bhadro purisājānīyo suṇāti: "
msgstr "One fine thoroughbred person hears about "

#. VAR: kālaṅkato → kālakato (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an4.113:5.4"
msgid "‘amukasmiṃ nāma gāme vā nigame vā itthī vā puriso vā dukkhito vā kālaṅkato vā’ti. "
msgstr "the suffering or death of a woman or man in such and such village or town. "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.5"
msgid "So tena saṃvijjati, saṃvegaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They’re moved to act by this, "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.6"
msgid "Saṃviggo yoniso padahati. "
msgstr "and strive effectively. "

#. VAR: paramasaccaṃ → paramatthasaccaṃ (mr)
msgctxt "an4.113:5.7"
msgid "Pahitatto kāyena ceva paramasaccaṃ sacchikaroti, paññāya ca ativijjha passati. "
msgstr "Applying themselves, they directly realize the ultimate truth, and see it with penetrating wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.8"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, bhadro assājānīyo patodacchāyaṃ disvā saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati; "
msgstr "This person is like the fine thoroughbred "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.9"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ bhadraṃ purisājānīyaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "that’s shaken when it sees the shadow of the goad. "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.10"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbred people are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:5.11"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, paṭhamo bhadro purisājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the first fine thoroughbred person found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc6
msgctxt "an4.113:6.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo na heva kho suṇāti: "
msgstr "Furthermore, one fine thoroughbred person doesn’t hear about "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.2"
msgid "‘amukasmiṃ nāma gāme vā nigame vā itthī vā puriso vā dukkhito vā kālaṅkato vā’ti, api ca kho sāmaṃ passati itthiṃ vā purisaṃ vā dukkhitaṃ vā kālaṅkataṃ vā. "
msgstr "the suffering or death of a woman or man in such and such village or town, but they see it themselves. "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.3"
msgid "So tena saṃvijjati, saṃvegaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They’re moved to act by this, "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.4"
msgid "Saṃviggo yoniso padahati. "
msgstr "and strive effectively. "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.5"
msgid "Pahitatto kāyena ceva paramasaccaṃ sacchikaroti, paññāya ca ativijjha passati. "
msgstr "Applying themselves, they directly realize the ultimate truth, and see it with penetrating wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, bhadro assājānīyo lomavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati; "
msgstr "This person is like the fine thoroughbred that’s moved to act "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.7"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ bhadraṃ purisājānīyaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "when its hairs are struck. "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.8"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbred people are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:6.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, dutiyo bhadro purisājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the second fine thoroughbred person found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.116, sc7
msgctxt "an4.113:7.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo na heva kho suṇāti: "
msgstr "Furthermore, one fine thoroughbred person doesn’t hear about "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.2"
msgid "‘amukasmiṃ nāma gāme vā nigame vā itthī vā puriso vā dukkhito vā kālaṅkato vā’ti, nāpi sāmaṃ passati itthiṃ vā purisaṃ vā dukkhitaṃ vā kālaṅkataṃ vā, api ca khvassa ñāti vā sālohito vā dukkhito vā hoti kālaṅkato vā. "
msgstr "the suffering or death of a woman or man in such and such village or town, nor do they see it themselves, but it happens to their own relative or family member. "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.3"
msgid "So tena saṃvijjati, saṃvegaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They’re moved to act by this, "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.4"
msgid "Saṃviggo yoniso padahati. "
msgstr "and strive effectively. "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.5"
msgid "Pahitatto kāyena ceva paramasaccaṃ sacchikaroti, paññāya ca ativijjha passati. "
msgstr "Applying themselves, they directly realize the ultimate truth, and see it with penetrating wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, bhadro assājānīyo cammavedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati; "
msgstr "This person is like the fine thoroughbred that’s moved to act "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.7"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ bhadraṃ purisājānīyaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "when its skin is struck. "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.8"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbred people are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:7.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, tatiyo bhadro purisājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the third fine thoroughbred person found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc8
msgctxt "an4.113:8.1"
msgid "Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo na heva kho suṇāti: "
msgstr "Furthermore, one fine thoroughbred person doesn’t hear about "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.2"
msgid "‘amukasmiṃ nāma gāme vā nigame vā itthī vā puriso vā dukkhito vā kālaṅkato vā’ti, nāpi sāmaṃ passati itthiṃ vā purisaṃ vā dukkhitaṃ vā kālaṅkataṃ vā, nāpissa ñāti vā sālohito vā dukkhito vā hoti kālaṅkato vā, api ca kho sāmaññeva phuṭṭho hoti sārīrikāhi vedanāhi dukkhāhi tibbāhi kharāhi kaṭukāhi asātāhi amanāpāhi pāṇaharāhi. "
msgstr "the suffering or death of a woman or man in such and such village or town, nor do they see it themselves, nor does it happen to their own relative or family member, but they themselves are afflicted with physical pain—sharp, severe, acute, unpleasant, disagreeable, and life-threatening. "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.3"
msgid "So tena saṃvijjati, saṃvegaṃ āpajjati. "
msgstr "They’re moved to act by this, "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.4"
msgid "Saṃviggo yoniso padahati. "
msgstr "and strive effectively. "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.5"
msgid "Pahitatto kāyena ceva paramasaccaṃ sacchikaroti, paññāya ca ativijjha passati. "
msgstr "Applying themselves, they directly realize the ultimate truth, and see it with penetrating wisdom. "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi so, bhikkhave, bhadro assājānīyo aṭṭhivedhaviddho saṃvijjati saṃvegaṃ āpajjati; "
msgstr "This person is like the fine thoroughbred that’s moved to act "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.7"
msgid "tathūpamāhaṃ, bhikkhave, imaṃ bhadraṃ purisājānīyaṃ vadāmi. "
msgstr "when its bone is struck. "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.8"
msgid "Evarūpopi, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhadro purisājānīyo hoti. "
msgstr "Some fine thoroughbred people are like that. "

msgctxt "an4.113:8.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ, bhikkhave, catuttho bhadro purisājānīyo santo saṃvijjamāno lokasmiṃ. "
msgstr "This is the fourth fine thoroughbred person found in the world. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.113:8.10"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro bhadrā purisājānīyā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti. "
msgstr "These are the four fine thoroughbred people found in the world.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.113:8.11"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

